<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/zenitram" rel="author">Zenitram</a> (<a href="http://mediaarea.net">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-21T07:20:20+01:00"><span class="date">le 21/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 07:20</span></time>.
