<a class="title" href="/nodes/96469/comments/1410474">Re: intuitive != d&#39;utilisable</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/zenitram" rel="author">Zenitram</a> (<a href="http://mediaarea.net">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-21T13:47:23+01:00"><span class="date">le 21/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 13:47</span></time>.
Évalué à&nbsp;<span class="score">
3
</span>.
</p>
<figure class="image"><img alt="" class="avatar" height="64" src="//img.linuxfr.org/avatars/137/013/000/avatar.png" width="64" /></figure>
<div class="content">
