<li class="comment odd score6" id="comment-1409939">
<h2>
<a class="parent" href="/users/ploum/journaux/moment-de-detente#comment-1409937" title="Aller au commentaire parent">[^]</a>
<a class="anchor" href="/users/ploum/journaux/moment-de-detente#comment-1409939" title="Lien direct vers ce commentaire">#</a>
 
<a class="title" href="/nodes/96469/comments/1409939">Re: intuitive != d&#39;utilisable</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/buf" rel="author">Buf</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-19T14:24:28+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 14:24</span></time>.
