<a class="title" href="/nodes/96469/comments/1409940">Re: intuitive != d&#39;utilisable</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/zenitram" rel="author">Zenitram</a> (<a href="http://mediaarea.net">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-19T14:36:53+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 14:36</span></time>.
