</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/buf" rel="author">Buf</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-19T14:12:29+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 14:12</span></time>.
